descriptionHtml:
Sorry boi, Sorry boi, Sorry boi.Â Oh no, look at that boi!

This is a inside joke mod for some friends, but if you feel the need for some wemonade, then download this .esp, put it inside your Skyrim/Data folder.
Then use console command "player.placeatme 000E0D67 1" without the quote marks obviously, then look down in game, and it should be at your feet. I reccomend doing the command on flat terrain.
author: Wemonade
